To work with the slider you first have to import the module which consists all features,
functions of the slider i.e.


[Module: kivy.uix.slider]





Basic Approach to follow while creating Slider â€“

1) import kivy
2) import kivyApp
3) import BoxLayout
4) set minimum version(optional)
5) Extend the class
6) set up .kv file (name same as the Slider.kv)
7) Run an instance of the class